# Nexploring UI — Project Structure

## Overview

**Nexploring UI** is a shared React Design System used across the Nexploring microfrontend ecosystem.

Its responsibilities include:

- Providing reusable, accessible UI components
- Managing design tokens and theming
- Distributing a tree-shakeable library via pnpm

The design system must contain **only presentational and composable UI logic**, avoiding any business or application logic.

All source code must live inside the `src` directory.

---

# Root Structure

```
src
|
+-- components
+-- tokens
+-- theme
+-- hooks
+-- utils
+-- styles
|
+-- index.ts
```

---

# Folder Responsibilities

## components

Reusable UI components. Each component lives in its own folder.

Every component folder must contain:

```
src/components/my-component
|
+-- my-component.tsx        # Component implementation
+-- my-component.stories.tsx # Storybook stories
+-- index.ts                 # Barrel export
```

Rules:

- One component per folder
- Export component, variant types, and props via `index.ts`
- Use CVA for variant definitions
- Use Radix UI primitives for complex interactive patterns
- Reference design tokens via CSS variables, never hardcode colors/spacing

---

## tokens

Design token definitions mapped to CSS custom properties.

```
src/tokens/colors.ts
src/tokens/spacing.ts
src/tokens/typography.ts
src/tokens/index.ts
```

Tokens define the contract between the theme and components. Components read tokens via `var(--*)`.

---

## theme

Theme definitions and the provider component.

```
src/theme/nexploring-theme.ts # Theme type, default values, CSS variable converter
src/theme/provider.tsx        # NexploringProvider (ThemeContext + CSS variable injection)
src/theme/index.ts
```

The `NexploringProvider` must wrap any consumer application to inject the design tokens as CSS custom properties.

---

## hooks

Reusable hooks shared across the design system.

```
src/hooks/index.ts
```

---

## utils

Generic utility functions.

```
src/utils/cn.ts             # clsx + tailwind-merge helper
src/utils/index.ts
```

---

## styles

Global stylesheet with Tailwind import and default CSS variable definitions.

```
src/styles/globals.css
```

---

## index.ts

Main barrel export. All public API surfaces must be exported from here.

Consumers import from `@gsrosa/nexploring-ui`:

```tsx
import { Button, NexploringProvider, cn } from "@gsrosa/nexploring-ui";
import "@gsrosa/nexploring-ui/styles";
```
